Subject: Re: [T2] RE: cutting holes for speakers

I prefer not to cut holes in door panels. I will only mount a speaker there
if someone has already hacked the door panel. My choice for speaker mounting
is the front kick panels. 6" round speakers fit nicely there and you don't
really 'kick' them!
